    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a affordable way to get on the road? This vehicle has plenty of character and is ready for someone with a mechanical touch to bring it back to its best! While it definitely needs some TLC and repair work, it offers a great foundation for a DIY enthusiast or anyone looking for a low-cost entry into car ownership. Grab a bargain and make this car your own!",
